Definition: a surgical procedure usually performed under local anesthesia in which the cervix is dilated and the endometrial lining of the uterus is scraped with a curet
Example: performed to obtain tissue samples or to stop prolonged bleeding or to remove small tumors or to remove fragments of placenta after childbirth or as a method of abortion
Synonyms: dilatation_and_curettage, D_and_C, operation, a, surgical, procedure, usually, performed, under, local, anesthesia, in, which, the, cervix, is, dilated, and, endometrial, lining, of, uterus, scraped, with, curet, to, obtain, tissue, samples, or, stop, prolonged, bleeding, remove, small, tumors, fragments, placenta, after, childbirth, as, method, abortion
Category: noun.act
